{"@class": "com.nd.elearning.sdk.resource.gateway.v5.bean.question.QuestionVo", "original_type": 4, "original_sub_type": "questions", "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "id": "c028b75e-a248-46c4-ac3e-0835400ef3e6", "type": 201, "content": {"preview": {"question_big": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/c028b75e-a248-46c4-ac3e-0835400ef3e6@3.pkg/1772597565584/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597566476", "question_small": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/c028b75e-a248-46c4-ac3e-0835400ef3e6@3.pkg/1772597565584/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597566476"}, "identifier": "c028b75e-a248-46c4-ac3e-0835400ef3e6", "feedbacks": [{"identifier": "showHint", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": ""}, {"identifier": "showAnswer", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<p>中华人民共和国主席是中华人民共和国的国家元首，其职权有公布法律、发布命令，任免权，外事权等；国家主席习近平签署主席令，任命李强为中华人民共和国国务院总理——任免权，A正确；在阿联酋访问的国家主席习近平，被授予阿联酋国家最高荣誉勋章——外事权，B错误；国家主席习近平签署发布特赦令，对九类服刑罪犯实行特赦——发布命令，C正确；国家主席习近平出席G20巴厘岛峰会，并与美国总统拜登举行会晤——外事权，D正确。故ACD理解正确，与题意不符；B理解错误，符合题意。</p>\n"}], "sequnce_number": 1, "description": "<p>下面对国家主席的职权理解<u>错误</u>的是（ &nbsp;&nbsp;）</p>\n", "title": "下面对国家主席的职权理解错误的是（   ）", "res_type": "$RE0201", "adaptive": false, "timer": {"timer_type": "sequence"}, "time_dependent": false, "responses": [{"identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "1-1", "base_type": "identifier", "cardinality": "single", "corrects": ["B"]}], "location": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/c028b75e-a248-46c4-ac3e-0835400ef3e6@3.pkg/item.json?v=1754813712602", "items": [{"min_choices": 0, "attachments": [], "columns": 1, "type": "choice", "choices_list": [], "associable_hotspots": [], "children": [], "hide_answer_area": false, "options": [], "orientation": 0, "multiple": false, "raw": false, "titles": [], "rows": 1, "response_identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "0", "max_